{"tid":245624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新界發生襲警案，警員頭上留兩血印送院送治","createTime":"2017-05-16T11:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T11:33:04.000Z","uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d95f7acc52e5da9dd9f297cafb37ed4b0cf4823","tid":245624,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"巴國總理今日訪港，香港警方嚴陣以待在多處布防以防恐襲。下午約1時，一名隸屬新界南總區交通部警員，被派駐守在長青公路在青衣隵隧道出口對開站崗，冷不提防遇到「空襲」，從天空飛來1隻巨鳥抓傷警員的頭部，頭上留有2條血痕，警方事後被安排該警員送院治理，傷勢並無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警員舜間被襲也來不及看清楚對方是何方神聖，只看到1隻巨鳥疑兇仍逍遙法外，在天空翱翔。<br />\n<br />\n香港觀鳥會麻鷹研究組組員葉志立表示，在上址出現的大型雀鳥，有可能是大嘴烏鴉、麻鷹或隼，大嘴烏鴉在天空飛翔的體型與一般麻鷹很接近，雀鳥襲擊人類很少見，牠們只會在感到有危險，或有人接近牠們育有小鳥的巢穴，才會主動攻擊人類。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1810000/1811794/MM_300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1810000%2F1811794%2FMM_300.jpg&h=54c78d83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29a0737f55f5bcff86b22d010ed450439410e0f7","tid":245624,"uid":90631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"交通警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bbb0a86cace5924841be2300ebb9b762a63e4b","tid":245624,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"狗都咁襲擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875c1c73a8c75882fb69004a237b9572d7e6c6a6","tid":245624,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗都敢襲擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}